<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الجذر:</span>ط ر د<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مثال:</span>في تقدم مُضْطرِدٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الرأي:</span>مرفوضة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">السبب:</span>لأنها من <span class="c2">«طرد»</span> وليس من <span class="c2">«ضرد»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الصواب والرتبة:</span>-في تَقَدّم مُطَّرِد <span class="c4">[فصيحة]</span>-في تَقَدّم مُضْطرِد <span class="c4">[صحيحة]</span> <a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">التعليق:</span> <span class="c2">(انظر: اضطرد)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>